headline: Domino's Pizza Shows Strong Q3 FCF - But DPZ Stock is Still Cheap
summary: Domino's Pizza generated strong FCF during Q3, and its FCF margins held up. DPZ stock still looks cheap, and its target price is 19% higher at $498 per share. Shorting OTM puts and buying ITM calls are good ways to play this.
